{"type": "article", "id": 21127, "title": "挂钩灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-22T07:30:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060711494920MAIizr4cJVFkUw.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tJaime Hayon 带来的壁灯像是将碗或者水杯粘在墙上了，主体用了抛光黄铜和磨光铝，里面安装有 LED 灯，贴在墙面上有点像挂钩。它也可以安装在天花板上，很灵活，让墙面变成一种装饰，配合着小巧的造型，很活泼。黄铜和铝材料本身是古典而传统的，但这个设计将它变得轻盈而有趣。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114947acVBHLoRANSJDKxZ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33374083\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071149483DGfXv7QIMj58gB0.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607114948uWwyifbEBa0Mr52Y.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}